prompt: Create a fitness center website which should track your calories and workout
refinedPrompt: Design and develop a comprehensive fitness center website that allows users to track their daily calorie intake and workout routines. The website should include features such as user registration and login, a personalized dashboard displaying calories consumed and burned, a database of exercises and workouts, and the ability to set and track fitness goals.
